NOTE ON UNDERLYING RECORDS: the dataset is a curated, validated
compilation derived from official German public registers (Orts- und
Gerichtsverzeichnis, PVOG, Bundesagentur für Arbeit, Destatis,
BayernPortal, OpenPLZ, xRepository). This license covers the
compilation, curation, normalization, enrichment, code and media
created by Amtsgraph; the respective terms of the official sources
govern the underlying records themselves (see docs/SOURCES.md).
